<http://model.geneontology.org/ev_w_id_REACTO_R-HSA-9908177_R-HSA-68819_R-HSA-3640874_component_BFO_0000051_REACTO_R-HSA-9908021_R-HSA-9908177_R-HSA-3640874_component_Reactome_R-HSA-4641257>
